### --- JOBS ---

### Add Frontend Developer Job
POST http://localhost:5000/jobs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyId": "<TechCorp_id_here>",
  "title": "Frontend Developer",
  "description": "React + Node.js Developer",
  "requiredSkills": ["JavaScript", "React", "Node.js"],
  "minCgpa": 8.0
}

### Add Data Analyst Job
POST http://localhost:5000/jobs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyId": "<DataSolutions_id_here>",
  "title": "Data Analyst",
  "description": "Python + SQL",
  "requiredSkills": ["Python", "SQL", "Pandas"],
  "minCgpa": 7.0
}

