### --- APPLICATIONS ---

### Alice applies to Frontend Developer
POST http://localhost:5000/applications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "<Alice_id_here>",
  "jobId": "<Frontend_Job_id_here>",
  "status": "applied"
}

### Bob applies to Data Analyst
POST http://localhost:5000/applications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "<Bob_id_here>",
  "jobId": "<Data_Analyst_Job_id_here>",
  "status": "applied"
}
